		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>You use a parry, a shield block, or some other action to make it harder for an enemy to hit an ally.</i></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>At-Will</b></p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Standard Action</b><b> &bull; Melee </b>1</p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Target:</b> One adjacent enemy.</p><p><b>Grant Bonus to Defenses:</b> You choose an ally. That ally gains a +2 bonus to all defenses against the chosen enemy's next attack. This bonus ends if it is not used by the end of your next turn. You can take the aid defense action only once to affect a particular ally's defenses. However, up to four creatures can take the action to affect the same ally's defenses.</p>",
